I16(I) $150,000; and

I16(II) $0.04 multiplied by the voting age population.

I77(ii) Voting age population

I14In this subparagraph, the term ``voting age population'' means in the case of a candidate for the office of Senator, the voting age population of the State of the candidate (as certified under subsection (e) of this section).

I18(C) Increased limit

