I14(ii) 4 times the threshold amount, but not over 10 times that amount_

I16(I) the increased limit shall be 6 times the applicable limit; and

I16(II) the limit under subsection (a)(3) of this section shall not apply with respect to any contribution made with respect to a candidate if such contribution is made under the increased limit of subparagraph (A) during a period in which the candidate may accept such a contribution; and

