I89. Contributions and donations by foreign nationals

I19(a) Prohibition

I11It shall be unlawful for_

I12(1) a foreign national, directly or indirectly, to make_

I13(A) a contribution or donation of money or other thing of value, or to make an express or implied promise to make a contribution or donation, in connection with a Federal, State, or local election;

I13(B) a contribution or donation to a committee of a political party; or

I13(C) an expenditure, independent expenditure, or disbursement for an electioneering communication (within the meaning of section 434(f)(3) of this title); or

