I12(2) a person to solicit, accept, or receive a contribution or donation described in subparagraph (A) or (B) of paragraph (1) from a foreign national.

I19(b) ``Foreign national'' defined

I11As used in this section, the term ``foreign national'' means_

I12(1) a foreign principal, as such term is defined by section 611(b) of title 22, except that the term ``foreign national'' shall not include any individual who is a citizen of the United States; or

