I89. Purposes

I11The purposes of this subchapter are to_

I12(1) measure more accurately the costs of Federal credit programs;

I12(2) place the cost of credit programs on a budgetary basis equivalent to other Federal spending;

I12(3) encourage the delivery of benefits in the form most appropriate to the needs of beneficiaries; and

I12(4) improve the allocation of resources among credit programs and between credit and other spending programs.

