I12(4) The Age Discrimination in Employment Act of 1967 (29 U.S.C. 621 et seq.).

I12(5) The Family and Medical Leave Act of 1993 (29 U.S.C. 2611 et seq.).

I12(6) The Occupational Safety and Health Act of 1970 (29 U.S.C. 651 et seq.).

