I89. Rights and protections under Americans with Disabilities Act of 1990 relating to public services and accommodations; procedures for remedy of violations

I19(a) Entities subject to this section

I11The requirements of this section shall apply to_

I12(1) each office of the Senate, including each office of a Senator and each committee;

I12(2) each office of the House of Representatives, including each office of a Member of the House of Representatives and each committee;

I12(3) each joint committee of the Congress;

I12(4) the Office of Congressional Accessibility Services;

I12(5) the Capitol Police;

I12(6) the Congressional Budget Office;

