I13(E) a national or State political party or any organizational unit thereof; or

I13(F) a national, regional, or local unit of any foreign government, or a group of governments acting together as an international organization.

I79(16) State

I12The term ``State'' means each of the several States, the District of Columbia, and any commonwealth, territory, or possession of the United States.

