I12(3) in the case of property that is not directly related to the purposes referred to in section 2081(a) of this title, dispose of such property by sale or other transaction.

I19(c) Requirements for conduct of transactions

I11In conducting transactions under this section, the Commission shall_

I12(1) accept money only in the form of a check or similar instrument made payable to the Treasury of the United States and shall deposit any such check or instrument in accordance with section 2083 of this title;

I12(2) in making sales and engaging in other property transactions, take into consideration market conditions and other relevant factors; and

I12(3) assure that each transaction is directly related to the purposes referred to in section 2081(a) of this title.

