I11The Capitol Visitor Center shall be used_

I12(1) to provide enhanced security for persons working in or visiting the United States Capitol;

I12(2) to improve the visitor experience by providing a structure that will afford improved visitor orientation and enhance the educational experience of those who have come to learn about the Congress and the Capitol; and

